      "content": "ugh just tripped while running and my ankle is super swollen. its pretty painful but i think i can just walk on it if i'm careful. should i just do the RICE thing (ice, rest, etc) for a few days and see if it gets better? i really dont wanna go to a clinic if i dont have to.",
