      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. honestly it hurts a lot more when i try to step on it and it feels kind of weirdly unstable, like it might give way. but i really dont have the time for an xray or anything right now. do you think it's really necessary to go in if i just stick to the icing and keep it elevated? i'm pretty sure it's just a bad sprain.",
